      "title": "Jaffna. 12 Indian fishermen arrested on the seashore",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "12 Indian fishermen have been arrested along with a boat for cross-border fishing in Sri Lankan waters.",
        "They were arrested by the Navy on Sunday evening on the shores of Jaffna, Parutthurai and detained at the Myliti fishing port."
